ZH: 这头牛是我们家的宝贝。
EN: This cow is the treasure of our family.

ZH: 这个农民养了一群牛。
EN: This farmer raises a herd of cows.

ZH: 牛仔们在草原上悠闲地吃草。
EN: The cowboys leisurely graze on the grassland.

ZH: 这头牛的毛色是黑白相间的。
EN: The coat of this cow is black and white.

ZH: 那头公牛很强壮。
EN: That bull is very strong.

ZH: 他们用这些牛拉着货运车。
EN: They use these cows to pull the cargo carts.

ZH: 牛奶是我们每天的必需品。
EN: Milk is a daily necessity for us.

ZH: 他们的生活和工作都离不开牛。
EN: Their lives and work are inseparable from cows.

ZH: 这个村庄的主要产业是养牛。
EN: The main industry of this village is cattle farming.

ZH: 牛肉是当地的特产。
EN: Beef is a local specialty.

ZH: 这家餐厅的招牌菜是牛排。
EN: The signature dish of this restaurant is steak.

ZH: 牛仔裤是用来骑马的时候穿的。
EN: Jeans are worn when riding horses.

ZH: 牧场上的牛群在夕阳下显得特别美丽。
EN: The herd of cows on the pasture looks particularly beautiful in the sunset.

ZH: 这头牛已经被驯化了。
EN: This cow has been tamed.

ZH: 牛角是牛的一种标志。
EN: The cow's horns are a symbol of its identity.

ZH: 牛的饲养需要大量的粮食。
EN: Cattle farming requires a large amount of food.

ZH: 这个城市有一座大型牛肉加工厂。
EN: This city has a large beef processing plant.

ZH: 牛肉富含蛋白质。
EN: Beef is rich in protein.

ZH: 这块土地非常适合放牧牛群。
EN: This land is very suitable for grazing cattle.

ZH: 牛作为农业生产的主要力量在农村地区得到了利用。
EN: Cows as the main force of agricultural production are utilized in rural areas.
